let's make a game!
name: Dragon Empire
author: Fenicf0x
desc: <b>Rise from hatchling to <t>Dragon Lord</t>!</b><br/><q>Hoard gold, breed dragons, conquer kingdoms!</q>
version: 2.3
created: 04/02/2026

Settings
stylesheet: stuff/bigBlue.css
building cost increase: 118%
spritesheet: cookieIcons, 48 by 48, https://orteil.dashnet.org/cookieclicker/img/icons.png

Resources
*gold
  name: <b>Gold Hoard</b> [<g#f90>[this]</g#>] 
  desc: <b>Shiny treasure</b> fuels your empire.<.>[?(gold>=10000|<i>Legendary hoard!</i>|<i>Need more...</i>)]
  icon: cookieIcons[0,0]

*eggs
  name: Dragon Eggs
  desc: <q>Freshly laid eggs ready to hatch.</q>
  icon: cookieIcons[1,0]

*wyrmlings
  name: Wyrmlings
  desc: <b>Baby dragons</b> - your growing army!
  icon: cookieIcons[2,0]

*fire
  name: Dragonfire
  desc: <#ff4400>Scorching flames</> from dragon breath.
  icon: cookieIcons[3,0]

*essence
  name: Draconic Essence
  desc: <#aa00ff>Pure dragon power</>.
  icon: cookieIcons[4,0]

Buttons
*hunt
  name: <t>RAID VILLAGES</t>
  desc: Dragons pillage for <g#f90>gold & eggs</g#>!
  icon: cookieIcons[5,0]
  class: bigButton hasFlares
  on click:
    $loot=random(2,8)
    if (have raidMasters) $loot=$loot*2
    yield $loot gold
    if (chance(15%)) yield 1 eggs
    toast <b>[random(50,150)] gold raided!</b>
  end

*incubate
  name: Hatch Eggs
  desc: Warm eggs with fire to breed army.
  icon: cookieIcons[1,0]
  req: fire 15
  cost: 4 eggs, 12 fire
  on click: yield 3 wyrmlings

Buildings
*lair
  name: Dragon Lair
  desc: <#f90>Cave system</> hatches eggs automatically.
  icon: cookieIcons[6,0]
  cost: 40 gold
  on tick: yield 0.15 eggs

*flamePit
  name: Flame Pit
  desc: <#ff4400>Roaring inferno</> generates heat.
  icon: cookieIcons[3,0]
  cost: 180 gold, 12 eggs
  req: lair 3
  on tick: yield 1.2 fire

*hoardVault
  name: Treasure Vault
  desc: <b>Impregnable gold storage</b> + production.
  icon: cookieIcons[0,0]
  cost: 900 gold, 25 wyrmlings
  req: flamePit 4
  on tick: yield 2.5 gold

*essenceAltar
  name: Essence Altar
  desc: <#aa00ff>Ritual site</> extracts dragon essence.
  icon: cookieIcons[4,0]
  cost: 4500 gold, 60 wyrmlings, 120 fire
  req: hoardVault 6
  on tick: yield 0.025 essence

*wyrmRiders
  name: Wyrm Rider Legion
  desc: <i>Elite dragon cavalry</i> conquers kingdoms.
  icon: cookieIcons[2,0]
  cost: 22000 gold, 250 wyrmlings, 12 essence
  req: essenceAltar 4
  on tick: yield 18 gold

*ancientLair
  name: Ancient Dragon Lair
  desc: <#f0f><t>DOUBLES all production!</t></>.
  icon: cookieIcons[7,0]
  cost: 90000 gold, 1200 wyrmlings, 600 fire, 60 essence
  req: wyrmRiders 12
  passive: multiply yield of :Buildings by 2

Upgrades
*reinforcedLairs
  name: Reinforced Lairs
  desc: <b>+50% egg production</b> from lairs.
  icon: cookieIcons[6,0]
  cost: 600 gold
  req: lair 12
  passive: multiply eggs yield of lair by 1.5

*fireproofEggs
  name: Fireproof Eggs
  desc: Eggs need <#ff4400>less fire</> to hatch.
  icon: cookieIcons[1,0]
  cost: 1200 gold, 60 fire
  passive: multiply cost of incubate fire by 0.6

*dragonTrainers
  name: Dragon Trainers
  desc: <i>Wyrmlings grow 2x faster.</i>
  icon: cookieIcons[2,0]
  cost: 3500 gold, 120 wyrmlings
  passive: multiply wyrmlings yield of lair by 2

*essenceRitual
  name: Grand Essence Ritual
  desc: <#aa00ff>Double essence from altars.</>.
  icon: cookieIcons[4,0]
  cost: 18000 gold, 25 essence
  passive: multiply essence yield of essenceAltar by 2

*raidMasters
  name: Raid Mastery
  desc: <b>Hunt yields 2x more gold!</b>
  icon: cookieIcons[5,0]
  cost: 45000 gold
  passive: multiply gold yield of hunt by 2

